puthiya vaarpugal is a 1979 tamil language feature film directed by p. bharathiraja . k. bhagyaraj and rati agnihotri played the lead roles in this film along with goundamani and g.srinivasan . the music was composed by ilaiyaraaja the film marked the debut of bhagyaraj as a lead actor . the film was remade in telugu as kotha jeevithalu . the movie was shot in picturesque locations in the theni area of tamil nadu .